# Add Clear Button to Search Input

## Goal
Add a "cross" (clear) button inside the search input box that appears when text is typed, allowing the user to easily clear the search query.

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [FilterBar.jsx](file:///c:/Users/barma/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/mess-khojo/client/src/components/FilterBar.jsx)

1.  **Mobile Input**:
    -   Add an absolute positioned button inside the relative container of the mobile input.
    -   Show only when `filters.location` is truthy.
    -   On click, clear `filters.location`.

2.  **Desktop Input**:
    -   Add an absolute positioned button inside the relative container of the desktop input (right side).
    -   Show only when `filters.location` is truthy.
    -   On click, clear `filters.location`.

```jsx
{filters.location && (
    <button
        onClick={() => setFilters({ ...filters, location: '' })}
        className="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600"
    >
        <X size={16} />
    </button>
)}
```

